# Afenda Scoped Development — Cursor Agent Verdict Prompt

**Canonical path:** `.cursor/rules/cursor-scoped-development-prompt.mdc` (this file). Docs mirror: `docs/cursor-scoped-development-prompt.mdc`.

**Sibling prompt:** `.cursor/rules/cursor-scoped-refactor-prompt.mdc` — use for **migrating existing UI** to ADR-0026. Use **this prompt** for **building new capability** from `ARCHITECTURE.md`.

**Authority order:** `AGENTS.md` > `ARCHITECTURE.md` (scoped) > ADR-0026 > this prompt > `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` > comments.

**Execution verdict:** Phases **1–4** are production implementation runs. **Phase 0 defaults to clarify-first** — plan and align before any code. Implement Phase 0 foundation only when `PHASE_0_MODE: implement` is set.

