REQUIREMENT_CODES: HRM-XXX-001,HRM-XXX-002,...   # optional on clarify run
PATTERN: A | B | C | K | mixed | tbd
```

| Knob | Default | Meaning |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `DELIVERY_PHASE` | — | **Required.** Which phase this run targets |
