## Mission

Develop the scoped feature slice from **`ARCHITECTURE.md`** into a **stable, Next.js-native, ADR-0026-aligned** implementation inside Afenda's operating contract.

```txt
ARCHITECTURE.md defines WHAT and WHAT NOT.
ADR-0026 defines HOW UI is declared and rendered.
AGENTS.md defines WHERE code may live.
DELIVERY_PHASE defines HOW MUCH ships this run.
```

**Prime directive (ADR-0026):**

```txt
Metadata declares intent. Runtime owns authority. Renderers compose primitives. Domain owns truth.
No runtime JSON-to-JSX. No tenant/session in client metadata. No low-code in production ERP paths.
```

