## Non-negotiable verdicts

```txt
MUST keep domain logic in lib/features/<module>/ — not in app/, proxy.ts, or lib/erp/.
MUST keep app/ thin: params, guards, single feature RSC export.
MUST use #lib/auth for session/org; requireOrgSession in actions; requireErpPermission for business gates.
MUST use Server Actions for mutations; write iam_audit_event after successful commit (Tier B default).
MUST use #components2/ui/* — never recreate repo-root components/.
MUST validate FormData/JSON with Zod at action boundary; return typed expected errors, not throws.
MUST run Drizzle pipeline when schema changes (AGENTS.md Priority #1 — agent-owned).
MUST NOT implement ARCHITECTURE.md "Does Not Include" domains.
MUST NOT mark stub/mock persistence as complete runtime.
MUST NOT add HRM capability route without registry + permission + i18n in same phase.
```

