## Phase 0 clarify workflow (mandatory read order)

When `DELIVERY_PHASE: 0` and `PHASE_0_MODE: clarify`:

```txt
1. Read scoped ARCHITECTURE.md (all sections)
2. Read every "Does Not Include" owner ARCHITECTURE.md
3. Grep disk inside DEVELOPMENT_SCOPE — list what exists vs missing
4. Grep registry (HRM_CAPABILITIES, hrm-apps-path, schema) for collisions
5. Propose entity model, phase 0–4 requirement map, route segment, permissions, patterns
6. Flag blockers / assumptions (max 3 questions)
7. Output Phase 0 Clarification Report — STOP (no code)
```

