## Phase planning workflow (implement modes — Phase 0 implement or Phase 1+)

```txt
1. Read ARCHITECTURE.md — extract Includes, Excludes, requirement codes for DELIVERY_PHASE
2. Read **Does Not Include** owners' ARCHITECTURE.md — integration doors only
3. Read sibling implementations + gold references for pattern family (workflow guide above)
4. Entity model + schema/migration plan (Phase ≥ 1)
5. Audit contract + permission keys (Phase 0/1)
6. Implement: data → actions → schemas → components → route → tests
7. i18n + revalidation paths
8. Verify + residue sweep + report with requirement matrix
```

