## Drizzle (when Phase needs persistence)

```bash
pnpm db:generate
pnpm lint:drizzle-journal
pnpm db:migrate:local
```

Commit schema + `drizzle/*` atomically. **Forbidden:** `db:push*`, hand-edited SQL/meta, human DB reset.

If Phase 0/1 can use existing tables via joins, prefer that over new schema — justify in report.

