pnpm lint:fixtures-parity                           # when messages/en.json changed
pnpm lint:renderer-contracts                        # when renderers touched
pnpm knip                                           # when new exports/routes/barrels
```

Follow `.cursor/rules/targeted-verification.mdc` when other agents run concurrently.

