| Status | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| `prepared` | Schema/contracts/routes scaffolded; runtime workflow incomplete |
| `partial` | Some acceptance criteria pass; gaps remain |
| `complete` | Requirement codes in phase implemented **and** verified |
| `blocked` | Concrete external blocker with evidence |
